		</div>
		<div class="col-xl-9">
			<!------------------ TOPIC ------------------>
			<h3 class="topic">
				<i class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard mr-5"></i> Event Management Dashboard
			</h3>
			<div class="row gx-md-5 mb-5">
				<div class="col-xl-6">
					<div class="card card-normal">
						<h3>Challenge</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>
								Defining the key, top-level data that most event
								managers need to see for tracking and managing a
								race event.
							</li>
							<li>
								Showcasing information in a way that is not
								overwhelming, visually pleasing and consumable
								at first glance.
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-xl-6">
					<div class="card card-normal">
						<h3>Process</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>
								Product owner defined specifications - The
								product owner initially defined all necessary
								items to showcase to the end-user
							</li>
							<li>
								Heuristics and Best Practices - I led the
								brainstorming of information architecture and
								presentation on the dashboard.
							</li>
							<li>
								Client Interviews - Immediate feedback was
								gathered from our first batch of users
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row gx-md-5">
				<div class="col-md-12 mb-5">
					<a
						class="card card-portfolio card-full card-big card-link card-long"
						data-bs-toggle="modal"
						data-bs-target="#galleryModal"
						data-bs-image="/images/work/rmrl/rmrl-event-dashboard@2x.png"
						data-bs-title={title}>
						<div class="row">
