								<h3>The Solution</h3>
								<div class="row">
									<div class="col-md-4">
										<p>
											Users have the ability to see the
											most common settings in one shot,
											which provides greater visibility.
										</p>
									</div>
									<div class="col-md-4">
										<p>
											Quick “edit” links, for easier to
											find settings. This provided better
											discoverability.
										</p>
									</div>
									<div class="col-md-4">
										<p>
											Universal Event Header and Sub
											Navigation - present on each event
											setting page, with key information
											and “quick jump” links.
										</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-12 img">
								<img
									src="/images/work/rmrl/rmrl-event-dashboard@2x.png"
									class=""
