			<!------------------ TOPIC ------------------>
			<h3 class="topic">
				<i class="fa-solid fa-chalkboard mr-5"></i> Event Results Detail
				Page
			</h3>
			<div class="row gx-md-5 mb-5">
				<div class="col-xl-6">
					<div class="card card-normal">
						<h3>Challenge</h3>
						<p>
							To present race event finisher information in a
							readable and searchable format. The biggest
							challenge is the amount of columns a data set can
							have, along with the possibility of a long list of
							participant categories. While this is already a
							challenge for desktop, it provides an even greater
							challenge for mobile view.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="col-xl-6">
					<div class="card card-normal">
						<h3>Process</h3>
						<ul>
							<li>
								Client Interviews - We analyzed what functions
								most athletes would utilize when looking at a
								results page
							</li>
							<li>
								Competitive Analysis - We jotted down the main
								components that made up other existing results
								services.
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row gx-md-5">
