					<a
						class="card card-portfolio card-full card-big card-link card-long"
						data-bs-toggle="modal"
						data-bs-target="#galleryModal"
						data-bs-image="/images/work/rmrl/rmrl-results@2x.png"
						data-bs-title={title}>
						<div class="row">
							<div class="col-md-12">
								<h3>The Solution</h3>
								<div class="row">
									<div class="col-md-4">
										<p>
											Designing and developing a UI for a
											webpage that is fast-loading,
											accessible and usable regardless of
											device type
										</p>
									</div>
									<div class="col-md-4">
										<p>
											The UI has all top level sections
											above the fold so the user can
											immediately spot the function they
											need
										</p>
									</div>
									<div class="col-md-4">
										<p>
											Only top finishers, per category,
											are present at first. Additional
											entrants are loaded via AJAX when a
											search is performed, or when
											pagination is triggered.
										</p>
									</div>
